name.k: ユー・マスト・ビルド・ア・ボート

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 癖になるパズルゲーム

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: The makers of the clever and addictive game 10000000 are at it again with an even bigger and wilder tile-matching, dungeon-exploring adventure. The pleasing mix of strategic depth and thrilling luck works beautifully as you make your way up a river, assemble an oddball assortment of crewmates, battle mythological creatures, and—you guessed it—build a boat. The retro graphics and jaunty chiptunes soundtrack are immediately charming, while defeating never-ending waves of monsters requires keen eyes and quick fingers.
